title: Getting Started with the DonorsChoose Data Set
description: This tutorial provides an overview of the DonorsChoose data set, as well as a quick-start guide to building your first model in TensorFlow and submitting your entry to Kaggle. For a refresher on machine learning fundamentals, check out Machine Learning Crash Course. For more practice building models in TensorFlow, check out the companion exercises.
